name: Air Canada 777-333ER [C-FIUW] Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Man, Air Canada has this bird in a bit of a rut! This is the second time I've filmed her this week, and she's been to YYC 4 times since the YYC-FRA route became a 77W! Anyway, here she is performing her third flight on this route. I also made a new outro for my videos, tell me what you think about it! I hope you all enjoy, and watch in 1080p!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
